## Oregon Liquor Sales in Multnomah


::: {.cell hash='OR_County_Parameters_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-2_456d6061c6a639d5f5361ec152864b34'}

```{.r .cell-code}
# Filtering for the county parameter
county_liquor_sales <- or_county_sales %>%
  select(-Month) %>%
  filter(COUNTY == params$county) %>%
  group_by(COUNTY, Year) %>%
  summarize(sum(Total.Sales)) %>%
  rename("Total.Sales" = "sum(Total.Sales)") %>%
  arrange(Year)
```
:::


 

